message: Two main strategies achieved 100 points: 1. Combine a 'liquid, filtered, mundane' with a 'liquid, extracted, magical'. To get 'liquid, filtered, mundane', use the 'filter' tool on a natural mundane liquid (e.g., morning dew). To get 'liquid, extracted, magical', use the 'vial' tool on a solid magical ingredient (e.g., sunstone, mandrake root, dragon scale). 2. Combine a 'liquid, extracted, magical' with a 'liquid, extracted, mundane'. To get 'liquid, extracted, mundane', use 'vial' on a solid mundane ingredient (e.g., amber, rose petal, bat wing, frog leg). Avoid using the 'vial' on gas items, as it creates negative value items. Filtering an already extracted liquid or a complex blend of extracted liquids often leads to 'poorly-filtered' items with low value. Pay close attention to exact item names for combinations.
